# Neonatal RAG Chatbot — Cursor Rules


## Stack
- Python 3.12
- LangChain + Ollama (local LLMs)
- Qdrant vector store (local embedded mode, no server)
- BGE-M3 multilingual embeddings (Arabic, French, English, Darija)
- BGE-reranker-v2-m3 cross-encoder reranker
- BM25 hybrid search alongside Qdrant
- Gradio UI
- SQLite database
- uv for package management (never suggest pip)
- ruff for linting and formatting


## Retrieval Pipeline
- Hybrid: BM25 (lexical) + Qdrant (semantic) → cross-encoder reranking
- BM25 index persisted at ./data/bm25_index.pkl
- Qdrant persisted at ./data/qdrant/
- Reranker: BAAI/bge-reranker-v2-m3 (multilingual, handles Arabic + Darija + French)


## Code Style
- Always use type hints on all functions
- Max line length: 88 characters
- Use Pydantic BaseSettings for all config
- Write docstrings for all public functions
- Prefer early returns over nested if/else
- Use ConfigDict(arbitrary_types_allowed=True) for Pydantic v2 models


## Project Structure
- All config in src/config/settings.py
- All DB logic in src/database/crud.py
- All vector store logic in src/vectorstore/store.py (Qdrant + BM25 + reranker)
- All RAG chain logic in src/rag/chain.py
- All prompts in src/rag/prompts.py
- UI entry point is src/ui/app.py


## Commands
- Install packages: uv add <package>
- Run app: uv run python -m src.ui.app
- Format: uv run ruff format src/
- Ingest data: uv run python scripts/ingest.py
- Run agent: uv run python scripts/run_agent.py